### Question 1

Based on 考察对 `return` 语句在 `finally` 块执行前生效的理解，以及 `finally` 块对变量返回值的覆盖规则。, answer this medium choice question.

### Question 2

以下代码执行后，最终返回值是多少？

public class FinallyReturnTest {
    public static int test() {
        int x = 10;
        try {
            x = 20;
            return x;
        } catch (Exception e) {
            x = 30;
            return x;
        } finally {
            x = 40;
            return x;
        }
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        System.out.println(test());
    }
}
- A. 10
- B. 20
- C. 30
- D. 40
